40
00:04:17,250 --> 00:04:18,170
Should have?

41
00:04:18,690 --> 00:04:19,290
No.

42
00:04:19,810 --> 00:04:21,360
I can't reach him now.

43
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:24,060
And he deleted me on WeChat.

44
