63
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,570
It's them?

64
00:05:31,290 --> 00:05:31,930
Liu Ming.

65
00:05:31,930 --> 00:05:33,680
This is my best friend, Wen Li,

66
00:05:33,770 --> 00:05:34,480
whom I told you about.

67
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,409
Nice to meet you.

68
00:05:35,409 --> 00:05:36,970
She just quit her job

69
