74
00:05:46,210 --> 00:05:48,000
You make me sound so bossy.

75
00:06:01,580 --> 00:06:02,140
Yingzi.

76
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,720
Dad, Mom.

77
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:05,320
Liu Ming ran away.

78
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,810
Liu Ming.

79
00:06:07,730 --> 00:06:09,290
He took one of my friends

80
00:06:09,580 --> 00:06:11,670
and went abroad.

81
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:17,010
[Liu Ming's mother, Yue Xiuqin]

82
00:06:12,790 --> 00:06:14,030
