84
00:06:16,230 --> 00:06:17,720
What happened?

85
00:06:18,210 --> 00:06:22,560
[Liu Ming's father, Liu Yiding]

86
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,360
Has he contacted you?

87
00:06:23,670 --> 00:06:25,550
Why can't we talk and solve them face-to-face

88
00:06:24,090 --> 00:06:28,450
[Housekeeper, Zhang Shilan]

89
00:06:25,570 --> 00:06:27,010
when things happen?

90
00:06:27,170 --> 00:06:29,880
