91
00:06:33,290 --> 00:06:34,130
This...

92
00:06:34,130 --> 00:06:35,040
Well...

93
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:37,720
Yingzi,

94
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,610
You don't know why Liu Ming left?

95
00:06:41,420 --> 00:06:42,620
I don't know.

96
00:06:43,290 --> 00:06:46,120
