97
00:06:47,690 --> 00:06:49,120
What have I done?

98
00:06:49,370 --> 00:06:51,170
You've been married for two years.

99
00:06:51,170 --> 00:06:53,170
So we've been waiting for two years.

100
00:06:53,370 --> 00:06:54,450
What have we been waiting for?

101
00:06:54,450 --> 00:06:56,010
His father and I are old

102
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:57,100
