103
00:06:57,250 --> 00:06:59,930
All we want are grandchildren.

104
00:07:01,030 --> 00:07:01,910
But we heard

105
00:07:02,450 --> 00:07:04,580
that you want to be a DINK.

106
00:07:04,660 --> 00:07:05,340
No.

107
00:07:05,980 --> 00:07:07,220
You want to be a DINK,

108
00:07:07,250 --> 00:07:09,250
