109
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:11,490
And we wouldn’t allow him either.

110
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:12,830
Well,

111
00:07:13,310 --> 00:07:15,360
a girl likes him

112
00:07:15,660 --> 00:07:17,470
