00:08:23,860 --> 00:08:26,330
♫It gradually becomes♫

131
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:30,840
♫a punctuation mark♫

132
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:31,090
My name is Luo Yingzi.

133
00:08:31,610 --> 00:08:33,010
I'm 28 years old.

134
00:08:33,890 --> 00:08:35,840
I just passed the bar exam

135
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:38,380
[Luo Yingzi]

136
00:08:34,549 --> 00:08:36,440
♫All the buildings♫

137
00:08:36,230 --> 00:08:38,010
